[I] A wrapper around Amtk for GNOME-style text editors like gedit

[T] libgedit-amtk is a wrapper around the Amtk library, used by gedit and
[T] similar GNOME text editors to simplify application menu and toolbar
[T] handling.

[U] https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/gedit/libgedit-amtk

